\cf3 \'a0\'a0 \'95 Miners "burn" coins to earn mining rights\cf2 \
\cf3 \'a0\cf2 \
\cf3 Future of Consensus Mechanisms\cf2 \
\cf3 \'a0\cf2 \
\cf3 \'95 Ongoing research into more efficient and secure mechanisms\cf2 \
\cf3 \'95 Hybrid models combining different consensus mechanisms\cf2 \
\cf3 \'95 Focus on scalability and environmental sustainability\cf2 \
\cf3 \'a0\cf2 \
\cf3 Conclusion\cf2 \
\cf3 \'a0\cf2 \
\cf3 Consensus mechanisms are fundamental to the operation of blockchain networks. While Proof of Work and Proof of Stake are currently the most prominent, the field is rapidly evolving. Understanding these mechanisms is crucial for grasping how blockchain networks maintain security, integrity, and decentralisation.\cf2 \
